*The following are plots of mean weekly visits of each type throughout the study period. Red and blue lines represent mean visits in areas exposed to the Getty Fire and Woolsey Fire respectively, while black lines are respective unexposed areas. We concluded that the parallel trends assumption held in all cases.*
